17 Section 1-116), is amended to read as follows:
18 Section 1-116. As used in this title:
19 1. "Teacher" means any person who is employed to serve as
20 district superintendent, principal, supervisor, counselor,
21 librarian, school nurse, athletic trainer, or classroom teacher or
22 in any other instructional, supervisory or administrative capacity.
23 The person shall not be deemed qualified unless the person holds a
24 valid certificate issued by and in accordance with the rules of the
