1 6. "Student teacher" means any student who is enrolled in an
2 institution of higher learning approved by the State Board of
3 Education for teacher training and who is jointly assigned by the
4 institution of higher learning and a board of education of a school
5 district to perform practice teaching under the direction of a
6 regularly employed and certified teacher. A student teacher, while
7 serving an internship under the supervision of a certified teacher,
