12 considered compensation for purposes of teacher retirement or the
13 minimum salary schedule;
14 7. "School nurse" means a person employed full time by a board
15 of education who is a registered nurse licensed by the Oklahoma
16 State Board of Nurse Registration and Nursing Education and is
17 certified the same as a teacher by the State Board of Education.
